{"tid":1572491,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"私了之後請大家提高警覺","createTime":"2019-09-15T16:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T18:18:36.000Z","uid":26015,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1608ae915b631de71f2d091036be7106f1d966ee","tid":1572491,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"以福建佬咁撚好戰同咁鐘意挑釁既性格<br />\n今次兵敗如山倒之後一定會好撚燥底同唔鋸<br />\n下次佢地好可能會升級武器(可能拎刀/鐵通之類)<br />\n大家絕對要小心自己落單私了主角變成手足<br />\n同埋盡量每次都要帶傘/行山杖呢D基本配置<br />\n如果見到有咩唔對路 例如唔夠人拿拿聲走<br />\n廢時真係比福建佬斬死<br />\n大家下次自重<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e2ae8d93e57111d2c1950603517730bb893598cf","tid":1572491,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:39:12.000Z","msg":"從今開始，文宣重點呢幾樣<br />\n1. 真普選係阻止今次事件出現既唯一辦法<br />\n2. 為私了同汽油彈做文宣解釋咁做既原因<br />\n3. 黨鐵點樣出賣港人，阻長警暴"},{"pid":"86a99e103c37554c549e29d4f54d8721d4180d44","tid":1572491,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:39:40.000Z","msg":"只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570141</a>"},{"pid":"bf2873499e18d0de5e2a1a419fbea282ff0a3dd5","tid":1572491,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:39:45.000Z","msg":"沙田已經有葬屍立刀出街, 小心!"},{"pid":"a957cfa8c369214aadbae76f0e0a9f655da88683","tid":1572491,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好一人行事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801dd5f90fbd8c5cc731e8d535fc8f97bc2a8b88","tid":1572491,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e3d90fe87de453b43c7a966df00e7d3e542fb92","tid":1572491,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:41:36.000Z","msg":"be first to drink<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Fr0hpm6.png\" data-thumbnail-src